- Stop.

56
00:04:25,098 --> 00:04:28,309
Kami adalah Tentara Revolusioner
Liga Komunis.

57
00:04:28,393 --> 00:04:29,727
Mohon jangan bunuh aku!

58
00:04:29,811 --> 00:04:31,521
Diam dan terus merunduk!

59
00:04:32,438 --> 00:04:33,731
Merunduk!

60
00:04:35,191 --> 00:04:37,527
Kita akan ke Korea Utara.

61
