Perjalanan bisnis kau sebut liburan?

632
00:46:16,857 --> 00:46:19,109
Kau mau ke mana? Bos ada di dalam.

633
00:46:28,410 --> 00:46:30,954
Mulai bicara! Kubilang mulai bicara! Hei!

634
00:46:33,999 --> 00:46:35,542
Cepat, Berengsek! Hei!

635
00:46:39,588 --> 00:46:43,217
Bicara, Bajingan. Kubilang bicara!

636
00:46:48,680 --> 00:46:52,434
Hei, kemari kau, Bajingan!
Katakan! Cepat katakan!

637
00:46:55,145 --> 00:46:56,313
Kau mau menemuiku, Pak?

638
00:46:56,396 --> 00:46:57,523
Hei, kau sudah tiba.

639
00:46:58,816 --> 00:46:59,983
Kerja bagus di luar sana.

640
00:47:02,736 --> 00:47:04,112
Mari bicara di kantorku.

641
00:47:05,447 --> 00:47:09,576
Hei! Cepat bicara, Bajingan!

642
00:47:11,703 --> 00:47:13,121
Berdiri!

643
00:47:38,272 --> 00:47:40,274
DIREKTUR JENDERAL HWANG GUKPYEONG

644
00:47:43,569 --> 00:47:44,736
Kau bawa apa?

645
00:47:47,239 --> 00:47:49,533
Aku bawakan wiski dan cerutu.

646
00:47:51,451 --> 00:47:52,744
Ayolah.

647
00:47:53,579 --> 00:47:54,872
Itu tak perlu.

648
00:48:05,799 --> 00:48:08,343
Sialan. Aku kena cipratan.

649
00:48:11,680 --> 00:48:13,056
Hei, aku suka itu.

650
00:48:13,640 --> 00:48:16,476
Pembajakan ganda. Ide bagus.

651
00:48:17,561 --> 00:48:18,896
Terima kasih, Pak.

652
00:48:18,979 --> 00:48:23,025
Para petinggi
tak bisa berhenti membicarakannya.

653
00:48:23,108 --> 00:48:24,693
PENERBANGAN 351 PEMBAJAKAN GANDA GIMPO
BAEK KITAE

654
00:48:24,776 --> 00:48:27,070
<i>PG, pembajakan ganda.</i>

655
00:48:27,154 --> 00:48:29,448
JAY351 MEMINTA PEMBAJAKAN GANDA
DI BANDARA GIMPO

656
00:48:29,531 --> 00:48:31,283
<i>Nomor kodeku, B73.</i>

657
00:48:36,038 --> 00:48:39,458
Aku memberikan nomor darurat KCIA
kepada ibu anak laki-laki itu.

658
00:48:39,958 --> 00:48:42,336
3, 8, 1, 1, 7, 7…

659
00:48:42,419 --> 00:48:46,381
Dan untungnya dia tetap tenang
dan menelepon nomor itu.

660
00:48:46,465 --> 00:48:48,717
6, 7, 1, B, 7, 3…

661
00:48:48,800 --> 00:48:53,221
<i>KCIA bergerak dengan cepat</i>
<i>dan sesuai dengan rencanaku…</i>

662
00:48:53,305 --> 00:48:56,808
<i>pesawat yang menuju Pyongyang</i>
<i>mendarat di Bandara Gimpo.</i>

663
00:48:56,892 --> 00:48:58,810
Bagaimanapun,

664
00:48:59,311 --> 00:49:00,729
soal Jo Manjae.

665
00:49:01,730 --> 00:49:04,232
Kudengar dia bertransaksi sabu-sabu
dengan yakuza.

666
00:49:05,567 --> 00:49:06,902
Ya, aku tahu.

667
00:49:09,988 --> 00:49:11,198
Kau tahu?

668
00:49:12,741 --> 00:49:13,742
Ya, Pak.

669
00:49:21,333 --> 00:49:23,585
Jadi, kenapa kau tak laporkan kepadaku?

670
00:49:24,252 --> 00:49:25,420
Pak Baek?

671
00:49:27,172 --> 00:49:28,256
Baek Kitae.

672
00:49:35,764 --> 00:49:36,765
<i>Itu benar.</i>

673
00:49:37,307 --> 00:49:38,767
<i>Namaku Baek Kitae.</i>

674
00:49:39,434 --> 00:49:42,354
<i>Kepala Departemen Intelijen,</i>
<i>KCIA Cabang Busan.</i>

675
00:52:18,218 --> 00:52:20,220
Diterjemahkan oleh Rio Wibowo

